------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


  The biggest increase, by 29.5 million kroons, took place in 
exports to Sweden. Fastest-growing were imports from Lithuania, 
which increased by 11.1 million kroons in one month. Exports to 
Russia decreased by 62.4 million kroons, and to Germany, by 34.2 
million kroons. Imports from Finland fell by 83.1 million 
kroons in a month, from Sweden by 34 million kroons, and from 
the Netherlands, by 32.7 million kroons. 
